You may have come across Shake Shack during your travels. It is a very successful restaurant chain, known for outstanding customer service. I recently listened to its founder, Danny Meyer, on a podcast with NPR’s Guy Raz.
What I heard was a masterclass in entrepreneurship, so I thought I should share some key lessons.



